headline: Lululemon Fashions Strong Growth Trend As Profits Cling To Highs
summary: Lululemon Athletica stock has been on a tear lately.  On Monday, Lululemon stock hit an important performance benchmark, seeing its Relative Strength (RS) Rating jump into the 80-plus percentile with an improvement to 82, up from 74 the day before.  The 82 RS Rating shows that Lululemon bested 82% of stocks for price performance this past year.
